feet alternate.

00:01:46.060 --> 00:01:50.440
So it is like a mountain climber here, really
pushing.

00:01:50.440 --> 00:01:56.690
As you are pushing here, you are working your
quads, your glutes, your upper body, and you

00:01:56.690 --> 00:01:57.889
