00:01:57.889 --> 00:02:01.020
30 seconds straight through.

00:02:01.020 --> 00:02:14.069
Then once we are up here what we want to do
is 2 feet together, we are going to hop.

00:02:14.069 --> 00:02:23.989
So take it in, and push, in and push.

00:02:23.989 --> 00:02:24.989
[Exercises]

00:02:24.989 --> 00:02:26.409
